typinglb.text: Whereas by the benefit of words and ratiocination they exceed brute beasts in knowledge, and the commodities that accompany the same, so they exceed them also in error.
You may serve the Speed Force, Flash, but I rule it. You are only a man, but I am a god, your god. I am Savitar!
I've never felt this healthy before. I've never wanted something rational.
